But we still understand sin and virtue only with our intellect.

00:24:00.805 --> 00:24:03.182
We do not want to do it because our mother told us that it is bad.

00:24:03.182 --> 00:24:07.647
We do not want to do it because our father told us to do it, or because it is written in the Gita.

00:24:07.647 --> 00:24:12.360
But that has not yet come into our consciousness.

00:24:12.360 --> 00:24:16.740
After Sahaja Yoga, it comes into our consciousness.

00:24:16.740 --> 00:24:22.031
That is, even if you say you can do it, you cannot do it. There will be trouble. Bring vibrations.

00:24:22.031 --> 00:24:27.758
If you try to do something, you will immediately get stuck in your head.

00:24:27.758 --> 00:24:32.927
It will happen automatically. You will not have to make any effort for it.

00:24:32.927 --> 00:24:38.548
When this Dharma awakens in you, you will not have to tell me. You will start it yourself.

00:24:38.548 --> 00:24:42.347
There was a householder. He used to smoke a lot.

00:24:42.347 --> 00:24:49.014
Even after Sahaj Yoga, he did not try. He could have quit in a moment. But he did not try.

00:24:49.014 --> 00:24:52.990
Now, since he had been smoking since childhood, he could not quit.

00:24:52.990 --> 00:25:01.113
Finally, he came to me and said, “Mother, when I sit in meditation, my mouth feels so big. I don’t understand whether I am becoming like Hanuman or not.”

00:25:01.113 --> 00:25:05.075
Now, should I tell you the truth? I know that you smoke.

00:25:05.075 --> 00:25:08.945
Going back. Sometimes you smoke like this, is it true or not?

00:25:08.945 --> 00:25:16.601
It is good to say, Mother. There is no doubt about it. Now I believe it, he said. now just promise me in front of me that you will not smoke.

00:25:16.601 --> 00:25:21.502
What is the point of hiding it from me? As soon as he said it, the tobacco suddenly quit and it was gone.

00:25:21.502 --> 00:25:30.446
Such things get quit in this way. Dharma is automatically awakened within. No need to tell, no need to work hard for it.

00:25:30.446 --> 00:25:41.738
I realized that this was the awakening of Dharma. Knowledge is that consciousness within you, within your personality.

00:25:41.738 --> 00:25:45.147
That consciousness must become conscious.

00:25:45.147 --> 00:25:55.228
This is what Krishna called “knowledge” and that is why he said that only through knowledge can you become like God. This knowledge.

00:25:55.228 --> 00:26:03.432
About devotion, he then said that if you want to do devotion, do it unwavering. That is very good.

00:26:03.432 --> 00:26:07.544
Give me the flowers, fruits, whatever you want. I will take it. When I take it, I take everything.

00:26:07.544 --> 00:26:11.945
When I give it, it is unwavering. Now, you see, there is a flaw in this word.

00:26:11.945 --> 00:26:16.591
Unwavering. That is, when there is no other.

00:26:16.591 --> 00:26:25.116
That is, when it has been enlightened. Only when it has been enlighted  devotion is fun. Otherwise, who do you call by calling them?

00:26:25.116 --> 00:26:34.041
As I told you now, there are many types of Sahaja Yoga.

00:26:34.041 --> 00:26:37.047
Infinite people have received infinite blessings.

00:26:37.047 --> 00:26:47.467
One of us had an architect. He said, "Mother, I used to worship so many gods, I used to worship so many goddesses, but I have eighteen worlds of poverty."

00:26:47.467 --> 00:26:52.740
When I came to Sahaja Yoga, he said, "It starts raining." What does "rain" mean?

00:26:52.740 --> 00:27:03.401
So, he said, they sent me to build special houses in places where it was raining a lot, and there was only money there.

00:27:03.401 --> 00:27:14.378
A very ordinary man. A farmer. He had a small farm. It was not even half an acre and a fisherman.

00:27:14.378 --> 00:27:20.064
Every day he would come to see me and bring me a beautiful garland of flowers.

00:27:20.064 --> 00:27:24.586
I said, "Dada, why are you spending so much? It is too much for you, Patil. Don't do this.

00:27:24.586 --> 00:27:29.494
I don't feel good about it." You know what I mean, mother, then why are you saying this to me?

00:27:29.494 --> 00:27:38.638
He said that half of my farm was completely wasteland. Half of the land means I use about half an acre of land.

00:27:38.638 --> 00:27:48.475
A man came to me and said, should I take the soil from this land? If I use this soil, bricks will be good.

00:27:48.475 --> 00:27:56.150
That is, if I mix a little of that soil and say, I start getting so much money from it, what is the meaning of a garland?

00:27:56.150 --> 00:28:01.335
In this way, the Lakshmi element that is in your navel chakra is awakened.

00:28:01.335 --> 00:28:07.157
That is why Krishna has said that you should do unwavering  devotion.

00:28:07.157 --> 00:28:11.653
Until you have a connection with God, what is the use of breaking these walls.

00:28:11.653 --> 00:28:21.467
So many warriors go. Look at their condition? Poverty. Their health is bad. They have cancer. Trouble in their throat.

00:28:21.467 --> 00:28:29.199
What kind of brains have those idiots cracked. What kind of things? Their condition like a beggar.

00:28:29.199 --> 00:28:35.000
Would Vitthal like this? But they have not yet had a relationship with Vitthal.

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:37.567
As soon as they did, everything changed!

00:28:37.567 --> 00:28:41.091
So they told them to do unwavering devotion.

00:28:41.091 --> 00:28:48.842
First get the Lord. Then that devotion becomes real fun. Otherwise it seems like something imaginary.

00:28:48.842 --> 00:28:52.732
Our children have abandoned the name of God.

00:28:52.732 --> 00:29:00.639
Because here we have to wake up at four in the morning, burn sandalwood, bathe God. What did he get from doing that? That's all he gets angry about.

00:29:00.639 --> 00:29:06.737
If he wants to drink alcohol, he drinks alcohol, he uses black money, he also uses black money.

00:29:06.737 --> 00:29:11.192
All kinds of businesses. All kinds of businesses. They just wake up in the morning and spend it.

00:29:11.192 --> 00:29:21.188
What did they get then? If they don't get anything, then why should we do this hard work? So they have concluded that there is no God.

00:29:21.188 --> 00:29:31.625
In Algeria, the elders, the elderly, are very much like Khomeini. They call them fundamentalists.

00:29:31.625 --> 00:29:38.110
And they used to cut off the hand of a person if he made a slight mistake.

00:29:38.110 --> 00:29:40.367
If someone did something, they would cut off his throat.

00:29:40.367 --> 00:29:47.462
They used to bury him in the sand, and beat him with shoes on top. They have started some kind of race.

00:29:47.462 --> 00:29:57.420
They have started it. Just like Khomeini. Extreme fanaticism. Seeing that, the children there became communists. They said there can be no such God.

00:29:57.420 --> 00:30:04.148
How can there be such an evil God? But only one of them came to our London and got realised.

00:30:04.148 --> 00:30:13.641
A boy. He immediately went and said that there is God. He is not even fanatic and he was not in the middle of saying no to him.

00:30:13.641 --> 00:30:21.168
And today we will be surprised, there are many educated, well-educated children of Muslims here. Five hundred children have got realised in Algeria.

00:30:21.168 --> 00:30:28.815
Then think about your children tomorrow in your society.

00:30:28.815 --> 00:30:37.465
To add to that, this is the time of Nikari. At that time, we should have unwavering devotion.

00:30:37.465 --> 00:30:47.807
Third is “Karma Yoga”, Shri Krishna said that whatever you want to do, you should place it at the feet of God.

00:30:47.807 --> 00:30:51.693
