00:30:51.693 --> 00:30:55.291
These are impossible things.

00:30:55.291 --> 00:30:59.499
Shri Krishna used to say impossible things. Impossible.

00:30:59.499 --> 00:31:07.442
Oh, no matter how much you say you placed it in the hands of God, but have you placed it? Because as long as the ego is there, it will not go away. That ego must go away.

00:31:07.442 --> 00:31:12.459
Now, if people want to give up the ego, they will have to fight with it. People see it from that perspective.

00:31:12.459 --> 00:31:18.798
Just like a balloon that gets hit, it gets bigger and bigger. Such a person gets a double ego.

00:31:18.798 --> 00:31:22.692
They say, ‘We have given up this, we have given up that, we have given up this.’

00:31:22.692 --> 00:31:25.959
Only the intellect seems to have been given up. Nothing else has been given up.

00:31:25.959 --> 00:31:35.930
People get such a false ego, and thinking that we have given up everything on God, they live in a lie. In delusion.

00:31:35.930 --> 00:31:50.116
That happens only when, this happens only when it starts flowing through your hands easily. And what do you say? It is flowing, it is going, it is coming, something third. You are the third.

00:31:50.116 --> 00:31:54.669
This consciousness is flowing, Mataji Kundalini is coming up.

00:31:54.669 --> 00:32:02.333
