00:32:32.131 --> 00:32:36.735
Then they say it is happening, it is coming and going. Now we have become witnesses.

00:32:36.735 --> 00:32:46.511
Until this happens, people should not remain in delusion and think that we have become very big dharmic.

00:32:46.511 --> 00:32:57.184
