00:33:10.595 --> 00:33:18.101
Just yesterday a householder came to me. He said, I think I have had a revelation. Who gave it to me? Our Guru. He said, look at this.

00:33:18.101 --> 00:33:25.368
Do you think you should tell me where this man's Kundalini is? Ah, I need that much knowledge.

00:33:25.368 --> 00:33:29.455
I cannot tell you that. Well, tell me where yours is. I cannot tell you that either.

00:33:29.455 --> 00:33:32.640
He said, then what was the realisation?

00:33:32.640 --> 00:33:38.632
Suppose a blind man's eyes are healed, if he says, "My eyes are healed," the doctor asks him, "Tell me how many fingers he has."

00:33:38.632 --> 00:33:41.247
I cannot tell him, but his eyes are healed. How can that happen?

00:33:41.247 --> 00:33:49.522
He has to see it, he has to understand it, he has to know it, otherwise how did your eyes heal?

00:33:49.522 --> 00:33:56.243
There are such gurus. He says, I have kriya. Why is that?

00:33:56.243 --> 00:34:04.834
A householder came, sat with both feet near me. He said, "Ah, you don't want to sit with Mataji like that, both feet. I know that, but what should I do? If I put my feet close like that, I would become like a frog.

00:34:04.834 --> 00:34:10.376
Why is that? Is that what our Guru said that if you become enlightened, you will become like a frog.

00:34:10.376 --> 00:34:18.650
Now, what will you become like a frog after becoming a human? Why a snake or a scorpion? Think about it simply.

00:34:18.650 --> 00:34:24.402
Do you fly like a frog, do you stand on your head, that means you don't even have your own balance.

00:34:24.402 --> 00:34:36.687
The body balance that you had achieved in the human body till now, has also been lost and beyond it, you started dancing wildly, flying like crazy, taking off your clothes - so what kind of stupidity is this?

00:34:36.687 --> 00:34:40.456
And that means we have got realisation.

00:34:40.456 --> 00:34:45.897
If a human being wants to cross over, then all the animals should cross over first. Why humans?

00:34:45.897 --> 00:34:52.728
Some people take off their sleeves. But even stupid people have their limits.

00:34:52.728 --> 00:35:01.639
Now if you have such wisdom, there is a supply department for you. Many people come prepared in this way.

00:35:01.639 --> 00:35:06.521
There was a gentleman in our Nagpur. I know him well.

00:35:06.521 --> 00:35:13.114
He was very popular in our boss's company, his father told him to do it somewhere.

00:35:13.114 --> 00:35:18.953
His father was also in our office. So the boss told him that it's okay, I will send him a personal.

00:35:18.953 --> 00:35:25.910
He went there and did fifty businesses. He did black market, smuggling, bigling, whatever he wanted to do.

00:35:25.910 --> 00:35:29.773
Then his father died. So he got property etc.

00:35:29.773 --> 00:35:34.102
He sold his wife's jewellery, sold the house. He did this and that and ran away.

00:35:34.102 --> 00:35:41.477
His mother came crying, what should we do now, we trusted him and gave him the jewellery. We took everything away.

00:35:41.477 --> 00:35:44.803
Now how can we go to the police when our son has stolen something like this and that.

00:35:44.803 --> 00:35:48.628
So the poor man went to his mother's house somewhere in Baroda.

00:35:48.628 --> 00:35:52.976
Now this gentleman has become a very big name. What is his name? He named him Gulab Baba.

00:35:52.976 --> 00:35:59.709
He named him Gulab Baba. He, his mother told me that he sent me a lot of money and money, everything happened.

00:35:59.709 --> 00:36:04.994
He gave us a house back. He wanted to send money. So I swore to him once. He said, "Tell me. Who are you? How do you send money?"

00:36:04.994 --> 00:36:14.111
I wrote in a letter. Then I came to know that this Maharaj is famous by the name of Gulab Baba. Gulab Baba. That is, he is a braggart.

00:36:14.111 --> 00:36:20.200
