00:36:32.543 --> 00:36:36.235
Now think about this. Does God know the horse numbers?

00:36:36.235 --> 00:36:41.338
But there were people standing in lines there.

00:36:41.338 --> 00:36:46.272
You will be surprised, thousands of people were with him.

00:36:46.272 --> 00:36:55.857
So now you can see for yourself the wisdom of man. All these types. Ghostly.

00:36:55.857 --> 00:37:01.544
